Subject: Midwest Mash - Whiskies of the Great Lakes
Description:
There are a significant number of craft distilleries in the Midwest region, come and hear what makes them unique from each other, how those whiskies are made. Then stay for a tasting!  The presentation will be open, but the tasting will be limited participation. 21+ and ID will be required. Sign up at Ops.
  Speakers include:Greg Williams - Track: Food  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
